ood to these hands."],[9042,9184,"But I made a choice."],[9255,9442,"I sacrificed their beauty"],[9442,9542,"for my family,"],[9826,10051,"and if anybody thinks less of me"],[10051,10151,"for that,"],[10231,10356,"well, then I pity them!"]],"24":[[12,104,"Whatever!"],[183,233,"Forget it!"],[262,429,"I'm not buying it."],[442,654,"You haven't worked a day in your life"],[654,821,"since you married Shawn"],[821,975,"15 years ago."],[996,1176,"And now you're expecting us"],[1176,1347,"to believe that..."],[1355,1643,"you were the head of a fashion empire."],[1735,1939,"Why would anyone give that up"],[1939,2122,"just to be a housewife?"],[2181,2339,"I became a housewife to"],[2339,2485,"protect his ego."],[2635,2736,"He pleaded me to"],[2736,2865,"quit my job and to"],[2865,2998,"stay home with the family."],[3023,3290,"I...I was only too happy to oblige,"],[3290,3436,"because I loved them."],[3490,3603,"And in their eyes,"],[3674,3799,"I...I was nothing but..."],[3874,4074,"to be used and to be thrown out."],[4316,4396,"And now you're out,"],[4421,4471,"Eve."],[4517,4600,"You're done with them."],[4646,4779,"Time to forget about the past,"],[4813,4946,"and focus on your future,"],[4992,5096,"then taking them down."],[5176,5259,"Right, the contract."],[5372,5488,"Forget about what she says."],[5501,5584,"Queen Corbelle wanted"],[5584,5689,"a collaboration,"],[5697,5872,"a very lucrative deal between ROGUE"],[5872,6001,"and Rockwell Intimates."],[6001,6089,"That's what I'm here for."],[6177,6277,"Here sign the contract."],[6281,6402,"A lucrative deal you said."],[6423,6502,"Very lucrative."],[6552,6664,"She had high praises for you."],[6664,6806,"It...would be an honor"],[6806,6873,"for me to collaborate"],[6873,6944,"with your company."],[7294,7415,"That's not what I said."],[7540,7761,"I hereby nullify this contract."],[7895,7966,"Don't you dare..."],[7982,8028,"No!"]],"25":[[25,91,"Ah!"],[91,137,"No!"],[838,975,"I will take away everything"],[975,1101,"that I ever gave you."],[1101,1209,"I swear to God."],[1247,1338,"You bitch!"],[1438,1505,"You're just doing this"],[1505,1589,"to get back at me!"],[1659,1693,"I'm gonna..."],[2093,2189,"Told you not to touch her!"],[2481,2527,"What?"],[2585,2623,"You have to let me"],[2623,2736,"prove myself sometimes."],[3278,3324,"Mike!"],[3407,3599,"Did you see what she did?"],[3687,3999,"She seduced Giovanni Cavolini!"],[4095,4350,"After she tore up Queen Corbelle's"],[4350,4421,"contract!"],[4462,4608,"You should put them in jail!"],[4629,4671,"Giovanni,"],[4671,4846,"I know you're the biggest sponsor"],[4846,4909,"for ROGUE."],[4929,5059,"But tell your woman to behave,"],[5059,5176,"or I'm telling Queen Corbelle."],[5238,5401,"I think given the circumstances,"],[5401,5538,"she would understand."],[5563,5789,"I also think that you got a message"],[5789,5889,"from Giovanni,"],[5930,6056,"telling you to not go through"],[6056,6143,"the contract."],[6185,6227,"And yet,"],[6260,6452,"you went through with it anyways."],[6544,6731,"That is not what I told you to do."],[6769,6969,"Okay, I'm not falling for your tricks."],[7036,7123,"Queen Corbelle called me"],[7123,7219,"and told me personally."],[7399,7461,"Give me my phone."],[8199,8270,"She called you,"],[8358,8416,"like this?"],[9071,9142,"No way..."]],"26":[[12,87,"No way..."],[867,917,"What is it?"],[946,1080,"Sir, just letting you know"],[1080,1163,"the reporters are ready"],[1163,1230,"whenever you are."],[1284,1380,"Got it, thanks."],[1505,1539,"Oh..."],[1643,1751,"We're this close,"],[1818,1897,"but no dice."],[1926,2035,"And what's a phone call"],[2035,2147,"supposed to prove anyway?"],[2181,2306,"Giovanni already has my number."],[2306,2431,"He could have told you any time."],[2444,2560,"You smug bastard, how..."],[2565,2786,"Just...check your call history."],[2836,2940,"Unless, of course, you didn't"],[2940,3061,"save my number."],[3424,3495,"Unknown number."],[3620,3716,"What's that supposed to prove?"],[3795,3924,"That's right, because I..."],[3924,4099,"changed it after I left Shawn."],[4208,4254,"Eve!"],[4279,4391,"Enough with the pretending!"],[4425,4550,"You're just making it worse!"],[4608,4675,"Just leave!"],[5230,5438,"And we are"],[5438,5651,"live from the Grand Maple Gala,"],[5651,5843,"where it seems there's a bit of buzz around"],[5843,5918,"the mysterious"],[5918,6051,"Queen of the Red Carpet,"],[6051,6106,"who sources say..."],[6106,6260,"Finally, I wanted to catch a glimpse of"],[6260,6343,"Corbelle."],[6410,6477,"Oh my God."],[6523,6585,"She is back."],[6585,6639,"What's going on?"],[6660,6727,"I can't believe..."],[6727,6798,"I'm getting a text."],[6798,6877,"There might be a fake"],[6877,6944,"Queen Corbelle."],[6956,7073,"Wait, camera three gotta get out."],[7073,7182,"No...it's our chance!"],[7182,7257,"Go to commercial, now."],[7257,7332,"We have to cut the cameras."],[7332,7411,"No...no!"],[7411,7461,"I'm here now..."],[7615,7899,"Yes, all the attention is on me!"],[8033,8170,"I'm gonna be a star!"],[8662,8808,"Sorry to burst your bubble,"],[8846,9079,"but there is no real Queen Corbelle"],[9079,9129,"here!"],[9154,9309,"We have an imposter!"],[9346,9430,"A stupid,"],[9438,9622,"delusional housewife who is"],[9622,9784,"just craving attention!"],[9784,9855,"No way!"],[9855,10051,"My God, she is pretending to be"],[10051,10118,"Queen Corbelle."],[10118,10231,"How dare she!"],[10231,10306,"She's done..."],[10326,10485,"She's done, for sure!"]],"27":[[4,183,"We have an imposter!"],[196,275,"A stupid,"],[283,462,"delusional housewife who is"],[462,608,"just craving attention!"],[817,846,"There!"],[871,971,"What are they talking about?"],[1026,1105,"That's Eve Corbelle."],[1130,1226,"Do they not recognize"],[1226,1280,"who she is?"],[1326,1488,"You knew her before she went"],[1488,1589,"into her retirement."],[1626,1876,"Not everyone is as lucky as you."],[1876,1960,"And some are luckier."],[2039,2193,"I mean, Giovanni stayed in contact"],[2193,2239,"with her,"],[2248,2348,"even after her retirement."],[2398,2510,"Look what a mess he's made..."],[2552,2648,"can't even keep her safe,"],[2686,2748,"two feet away."],[3086,3211,"We can't let that filth ruin"],[3211,3319,"Corbelle's reputation."],[3411,3645,"That is quite a gamble,"],[3645,3766,"Karen Bradley."],[3787,3958,"I mean, aren't you the least bit"],[3958,4045,"concerned..."],[4083,4179,"about the fallout if"],[4179,4333,"what you say isn't true?"],[4466,4612,"Dang, the way she talks..."],[4683,4800,"She really does sound like"],[4800,4871,"Queen Corbelle."],[5005,5134,"Uh, what am I thinking?"],[5159,5246,"I can't fall for it."],[5246,5484,"I have to prove to her that I'm smarter"],[5509,5601,"than Giovanni."],[5609,5726,"You should be the one worried about"],[5726,5839,"your reputation."],[5847,5893,"Yeah!"],[6035,6272,"You might have slept with Giovanni,"],[6272,6389,"but the rest of us..."],[6418,6448,"Uh?"],[6448,6577,"We're not so easy to play."],[6598,6631,"Okay?"],[6644,6898,"And you ripped up Shawn Rockwell's"],[6898,6973,"contract,"],[6973,7173,"which is an insult to Queen Corbelle,"],[7173,7369,"and the world of fashion!"],[7428,7549,"I have already told you,"],[7603,7653,"okay?"],[7678,7924,"I am just friends with Giovanni."],[7999,8320,"I will sue you and you will lose."]],"28":[[0,145,"I will sue you"],[145,279,"and you will lose."],[279,446,"You just cut the theatrics, okay?"],[525,600,"We've seen"],[638,817,"all the evidence we need to see"],[859,934,"with you two."],[950,1113,"He wouldn't be covering for you"],[1222,1297,"if you didn't give him a little"],[1297,1368,"something something"],[1368,1472,"on the side, right?"],[1547,1730,"I am Eve Corbelle,"],[1801,1939,"Queen of the Red Carpet,"],[1939,2110,"whether you like it or not."],[2185,2352,"“I am Eve Corbelle,"],[2369,2477,"Queen of the Red Carpet,"],[2477,2615,"whether you like it or not.”"],[2744,2877,"And I'm the Queen of England!"],[3115,3278,"This is ridiculous."],[3278,3478,"Look, you've been a housewife."],[3511,3682,"A housewife"],[3703,3883,"for 16 years."],[3920,4012,"You've been scrubbing"],[4012,4074,"and cleaning"],[4095,4208,"the grime out of"],[4208,4375,"the grout of my shower!"],[4412,4475,"Okay?"],[4529,4679,"Just knock this off and leave."],[4679,4783,"The dishes are piling up"],[4783,4838,"back home."],[4859,4938,"Who is this guy?"],[4938,4971,"Giovanni"],[4971,5088,"is letting his girlfriend"],[5088,5205,"pretend to be Queen Corbelle"],[5205,5276,"when she's gone?"],[5276,5392,"I'm selling my stocks right now."],[5392,5451,"ROGUE is..."],[5451,5572,"It's ridiculous!"],[5572,5630,"I'm selling."],[5630,5739,"Yeah, better sell stocks"],[5739,5809,"before it plummets."],[5809,5851,"Sold."],[5851,5935,"No, they're sold."],[5935,5980,"That's it."],[5980,6135,"Giovanni, look what you've done!"],[6135,6243,"Our stocks are dropping"],[6243,6335,"by the second!"],[6335,6414,"Are you still gonna protect"],[6414,6514,"your little mistress?"],[6535,6702,"Queen Corbelle's got a lot of shares."],[6735,6856,"Get your woman to leave,"],[6873,6998,"or you're done!"],[6998,7090,"Do you want me to kick your ass?"],[7090,7144,"It's okay."],[7228,7323,"I've got it from here."],[7515,7570,"What is it"],[7570,7665,"that I could do"],[7665,7745,"to prove to you"],[7745,7841,"who I really am?"],[7920,8041,"You just never give up, do you?"],[8354,8433,"How about this?"],[8479,8537,"Queen Corbelle"],[8537,8692,"once helped an up and coming actor"],[8692,8787,"land a big role,"],[8787,8904,"and now he's one of the biggest names"],[8904,8996,"in the film industry."],[9034,9163,"Bring him to the gala."],[9225,9338,"Then I'll believe you."],[9401,9476,"You're talking about"],[9476,9580,"Leonardo Harrington."],[9622,9709,"Okay, sure."],[10235,10293,"Let's go."],[10293,10389,"Corbelle needs our help."],[10598,10652,"Actually,"],[10677,10723,"Anna,"],[10810,10906,"can you make sure to grab"],[10906,11002,"a copy of"],[11002,11081,"ROGUE magazine"],[11081,11215,"that I keep on the coffee table."],[11248,11307,"Yes."],[11307,11348,"We'll do."],[12020,12087,"Queen Corbelle."],[12216,12291,"Yeah, I've waited years"],[12291,12374,"to hear back from you."],[12458,12554,"Give me 10 minutes."],[12554,12675,"I'll be there as soon as I can."],[12825,12925,"No way."],[12925,13017,"Leonardo Harrington"],[13017,13179,"hates events like these."],[13179,13363,"He hasn't shown up to the gala in years."],[13405,13509,"Is she really gonna get him here"],[13509,13638,"with a phone call?"],[13734,13792,"No."],[13792,13909,"Was I wrong about her?"]],"29":[[4,162,"If you could please"],[162,417,"just give us a little bit more time,"],[467,629,"and I will prove to you"],[629,875,"that your trust in ROGUE"],[875,1001,"is not in vain."],[1109,1155,"Eve..."],[1192,1322,"what would ROGUE do without you?"],[1430,1576,"The way she carries herself..."],[1634,1735,"Could she really be the Queen"],[1735,1814,"of the Red Carpet?"],[1868,2085,"So you've always this stunning?"],[2177,2385,"I hate her!"],[2444,2665,"Why is she getting all the attention?"],[2698,2844,"She's a fake!"],[2844,3007,"I'm telling you!"],[3169,3257,"Again"],[3257,3374,"with the fake"],[3374,3495,"phone calls?"],[3495,3741,"You've already tried this stunt with Mike."],[3787,3999,"And now you're saying"],[3999,4099,"that, that was"],[4099,4254,"Leonardo Harrington?"],[4683,4788,"We're not stupid."],[4854,5084,"Why would we believe you?"],[5242,5359,"10 minutes."],[5359,5559,"That is all I ask for."],[5597,5793,"You heard that he was on his way."],[5864,6068,"What is a little bit more time?"],[6068,6364,"Or are you just scared?"],[6527,6735,"I'm not scared of you."],[6802,7048,"Of course you're not Queen Corbelle."],[7048,7194,"You're a housewife."],[7261,7382,"I just..."],[7382,7674,"I just think you're wasting our time."]],"30":[[8,112,"Maybe she's right."],[112,246,"Leonardo Harrington hates events"],[246,283,"like this."],[283,392,"He hasn't shown up to one in years."],[392,479,"Yeah, he doesn't even take"],[479,563,"high paying jobs"],[563,725,"if he doesn't like the director."],[725,934,"There's no way he's at her beck and call."],[1217,1301,"Hold on, hold on."],[1455,1505,"Eve,"],[1505,1593,"Karen's right."],[1651,1785,"What happened to the sweet,"],[1830,1960,"subservient"],[2014,2127,"woman that I married?"],[2252,2535,"You're just wasting everyone's time here."],[3153,3261,"I don't think so."],[4617,4763,"Queen Corbelle,"],[4763,4904,"I'm so sorry to keep you waiting."],[5363,5467,"Holy shit!"],[5467,5576,"It's Leonardo."],[5601,5697,"Are we getting this?"],[5697,5868,"So this is the real Queen Corbelle?"],[5868,5960,"Is she really back?"]],"31":[[412,558,"Queen Corbelle,"],[558,700,"I'm so sorry to keep you waiting."],[905,1126,"Sixteen years,"],[1126,1222,"and you are just"],[1222,1363,"as much of a show-off now"],[1363,1468,"as you were back then."],[1847,2014,"Well, you're the one and only"],[2014,2110,"Queen Corbelle."],[2110,2256,"It's only fitting with your status."],[2585,2715,"Not so fast superstar."],[2715,2861,"Aren't you here to do something"],[2861,2940,"more important?"],[3011,3078,"Of course."],[3115,3265,"I'm here to defend her honor"],[3307,3453,"after you failed to do so."],[3553,3611,"Okay."],[3741,3878,"Is my presence here"],[3916,4049,"not proof enough of"],[4049,4237,"Queen Corbelle's identity?"],[4441,4512,"What?"],[4567,4833,"That's the real Leonardo Harrington."],[4909,5180,"So all this time Eve was..."],[5209,5347,"You're really her?"],[5347,5480,"You're Queen Corbelle?"],[5572,5697,"Oh, no, what have I done?"]],"32":[[12,233,"That's the real Queen Corbelle."],[266,442,"Leonardo Harrington just said it."],[442,533,"It's her."],[533,667,"Which means"],[667,784,"we've been insulting"],[784,909,"the Queen of the Red Carpet"],[909,1088,"this whole time!"],[1172,1309,"What am I gonna do?"],[1309,1514,"Well then, that settles it."],[1514,1680,"I think an apology is in order,"],[1751,1847,"that is unless"],[1847,2002,"you all want to be blacklisted"],[2002,2102,"from the industry."],[2102,2235,"Wait, no, no, wait."],[2273,2369,"Queen Corbelle,"],[2369,2427,"please listen,"],[2427,2485,"I'll quit."],[2485,2610,"I don't even deserve to be your editor."],[2610,2781,"Just just forgive me."],[2781,2919,"Queen Corbelle, please..."],[2919,3073,"My family works in gemstones."],[3073,3144,"I'll give you"],[3144,3336,"the first pick of next year's jewels"],[3336,3440,"and..."],[3440,3557,"I will even donate"],[3557,3699,"the entire red diamond collection"],[3699,3762,"to ROGUE."],[3762,3908,"I'll give you my art collection."],[3908,4054,"I'll give you the whole gallery if you want."],[4054,4129,"Just just..."],[4129,4241,"please don't take it out on us,"],[4241,4270,"please!"],[4270,4320,"Forgive us!"],[4320,4437,"I'll do anything!"],[4437,4483,"Okay."],[4483,4521,"Come on."],[4521,4567,"Stop."],[4567,4658,"Oh, no..."],[5138,5259,"Eve..."],[5259,5455,"you really the Queen of the Red Carpet?"],[5897,6001,"Like I'm an idiot..."],[6043,6322,"I realize now how much you gave up"],[6322,6569,"to be my wife and to raise our..."],[6569,6648,"our kid."],[6773,6965,"Didn't realize how much you love me."],[7019,7140,"You know, I think we should just give it"],[7140,7253,"one more chance."]],"33":[[50,179,"Can we give it another cha..."],[204,350,"Back off!"],[350,454,"Don't you ever"],[454,567,"forget how you hurt her!"],[625,709,"What I'll do to you"],[709,842,"if you ever mess with her again!"],[871,971,"Shawn,"],[971,1188,"you don't deserve a woman like her."],[1188,1313,"You think Queen Corbelle's"],[1313,1388,"gonna take you back"],[1388,1559,"just because you said sorry?"],[1559,1701,"Who do you think you are?"],[1701,1814,"Who do you think she is?"],[1839,1951,"You're way out of"],[1951,2085,"Queen Corbelle's league!"],[2085,2214,"You can't just cheat on her"],[2214,2373,"and then expect her forgiveness!"],[2435,2519,"Shame on you,"],[2519,2631,"Shawn Rockwell!"],[2631,2686,"Yeah!"],[2686,2798,"Hey, just..."],[2998,3061,"Look,"],[3098,3165,"Eve,"],[3165,3257,"I've never"],[3257,3440,"signed the divorce papers,"],[3503,3712,"so I am still legally"],[3749,3941,"your lawfully bound husband."],[4016,4112,"So let's just"],[4137,4279,"start over and try again."],[4283,4425,"That reminds me."],[4425,4612,"The divorce papers are in the mail."],[4671,4833,"Sign them and return them to me"],[4833,4921,"ASAP."],[4988,5117,"No, no, I..."],[5117,5226,"I won't sign them."],[5372,5497,"Hear that I won't"],[5497,5609,"sign them."],[5609,5822,"I mean, yeah, I admit that cheating is..."],[5822,5972,"kind of my fault, but..."],[6114,6193,"That's no big deal."],[6193,6327,"That's water under the bridge."],[6431,6569,"We've had sixteen years of"],[6569,6673,"marriage."],[6760,6940,"You can't just put sixteen years of love"],[6940,7032,"down the drain."],[7307,7415,"We are over!"],[7528,7645,"It's too late,"],[7645,7749,"Mr. Rockwell."],[8053,8120,"Well..."],[8120,8370,"I'm not buying it."],[8370,8575,"If she was the real Queen"],[8575,8687,"of the Red Carpet,"],[8687,8821,"why would she just"],[8821,9042,"let us insult her like that?"],[9042,9121,"Shawn, you have to..."],[9121,9225,"Shut up, woman!"],[9225,9392,"I... I cannot stand you!"],[9392,9588,"This is all your fault!"]],"34":[[54,141,"Shawn!"],[141,271,"Did you just"],[271,371,"slap me?"],[371,450,"Oh yeah!"],[450,542,"I slapped you!"],[542,633,"I slapped you good!"],[633,750,"This is all of your fault!"],[750,817,"She..."],[834,1017,"she seduced me."],[1017,1167,"She drew me right in!"],[1167,1347,"And then she got me the invite to this gala!"],[1347,1438,"And I would never have said"],[1438,1518,"those things about you."],[1518,1680,"I would never have said them about you,"],[1680,1851,"if she hadn't tricked me!"],[2281,2373,"It's quite a show"],[2373,2610,"you're putting on for the camera, Shawn."],[2715,2781,"We've hit gold!"],[2781,2890,"...on the edge of my seat!"],[2890,2969,"The ratings on the network"],[2969,3023,"are gonna blow up."],[3023,3107,"This is insane!"],[3123,3253,"Oh my God, yeah no."],[3561,3720,"Wait, hold on."],[3803,4108,"Leonardo Harrington has stocks"],[4108,4191,"in ROGUE."],[4291,4425,"How do we know that"],[4425,4491,"he's just"],[4491,4617,"siding with Eve"],[4617,4813,"for his own financial interest?"],[4904,5021,"Wait, so what you're saying is"],[5021,5234,"pretending that Eve is the real"],[5234,5367,"Queen Corbelle,"],[5367,5467,"so he won't lose money"],[5467,5651,"in his ROGUE stocks?"],[5651,5722,"Either that or"],[5722,5935,"she's sleeping with him too."],[5964,6227,"They're suspiciously close."]],"35":[[8,225,"She's sleeping with him too."],[346,575,"They're suspiciously close."],[575,746,"No... no way."],[746,913,"Queen Corbelle would never do that."],[1259,1301,"Yeah."],[1376,1547,"But an imposter would."],[1851,1918,"Wouldn't she?"],[1956,2097,"And Eve"],[2097,2285,"would do anything"],[2285,2410,"for money"],[2410,2502,"and power."],[2811,2969,"Maybe Miss Bradley is right!"],[3048,3178,"The stocks have been going up"],[3178,3345,"ever since Leonardo got here."],[3345,3486,"It's at an all-time high."],[3653,3845,"Giovanni and Leonardo"],[3845,3962,"working together?"],[4016,4154,"Is this a publicity stunt?"],[4358,4425,"Look at them."],[4517,4646,"Idiots, all of them."],[4708,4775,"But it's okay."],[4775,4859,"I came prepared."],[4946,5096,"She should be here about now."],[5096,5184,"Wh... what?"],[5292,5347,"Who?"],[5347,5413,"Me."],[5530,5751,"I can prove Queen Corbelle's identity."]],"36":[[241,379,"Here you go, Mr. Harrington."],[379,550,"I sent another copy backstage."],[608,721,"Right on time, Anna."],[1401,1488,"What is this?"],[1530,1630,"Well, it's the only picture that"],[1630,1739,"shows your face."],[1739,1872,"But I have other copies,"],[1872,1947,"so don't worry."],[1985,2089,"I figured these clowns"],[2089,2227,"wouldn't go down so easy,"],[2310,2535,"so I had Anna bring it to me."],[2535,2648,"Why don't you forget about Leonardo"],[2648,2723,"right now?"],[3232,3453,"I think you know exactly what to do."],[3661,3757,"It's your time to shine."],[4829,4963,"All set, Mr. Harrington."],[5146,5267,"It's ROGUE magazine."],[5868,5980,"Oh..."],[6406,6510,"Wait, wait, that's..."],[6548,6664,"that's...Eve."],[6998,7040,"It's her."],[7040,7136,"What?"],[7161,7294,"She is Queen Corbelle."]],"37":[[1026,1113,"No!"],[1226,1313,"It..."],[1313,1380,"it can't be."],[1380,1522,"There's no way that"],[1522,1726,"Eve is Queen Corbelle."],[1726,1906,"She's supposed to be a stupid,"],[1906,2068,"good-for-nothing housewife."],[2068,2147,"How dare you!"],[2206,2423,"Queen Corbelle may not be royal by birth,"],[2531,2627,"but her charm"],[2677,2786,"and business prowess"],[2786,2890,"got her a full scholarship"],[2890,2965,"to Harvard."],[3090,3249,"And she's the founder"],[3249,3449,"of ROGUE and Grand Maple Gala."],[3449,3657,"She built this entire empire."],[3770,3849,"And you're just..."],[3916,4070,"her husband's sidepiece."],[4108,4141,"I..."],[4141,4300,"There's... there's no..."],[4300,4537,"I... I don't mean to insult the Queen!"],[4537,4617,"It's just that..."],[4671,4804,"It can't be Eve!"],[4829,4929,"Yeah, yeah, yeah!"],[4929,5005,"That's it!"],[5109,5217,"If she was really the Queen"],[5217,5317,"of the Red Carpet,"],[5363,5588,"then why didn't she tell her husband,"],[5588,5655,"me!"],[5755,5922,"I mean my business has gone through"],[5922,6022,"some ups and downs."],[6022,6126,"She could have completely just..."],[6126,6256,"You never realized,"],[6310,6439,"you dumb fuck,"],[6485,6648,"that every time your little business"],[6648,6765,"had a problem,"],[6815,6940,"all you had to do was complain to Eve"],[6940,7102,"and magically disappeared."],[7157,7278,"This is how you repay her?"],[7357,7478,"She made a home for you."],[7478,7624,"She took care of your child."],[7624,7741,"Giovanni, it's no use."],[7824,7995,"Ungrateful leeches like him?"],[8045,8153,"They never change."],[8187,8258,"No!"],[8258,8395,"No, I don't believe you!"]],"38":[[4,154,"No, I don't believe you!"],[254,500,"Okay, I'm here because I'm good!"],[629,721,"Because I made"],[721,971,"excellent executive business decisions!"],[971,1213,"Because I am very smart!"],[1343,1539,"You think my wife did that for me?"],[1626,1693,"Come on!"],[1797,1889,"Sure you did."],[1943,2106,"And I'll just go ahead and pull all"],[2106,2327,"your financial funding since"],[2327,2781,"you said you're so good and so smart."],[2781,2898,"No, no way!"],[2932,3053,"You can't do that!"],[3053,3178,"They won't let you!"],[3866,3945,"Please."],[3962,4037,"Phone call."],[4037,4120,"Another one."],[4124,4208,"Hello?"],[4275,4466,"Please inform all companies"],[4466,4696,"that we will no longer be doing business with"],[4696,4825,"Rockwell Intimates"],[4863,5155,"and cancel all future engagements"],[5155,5263,"with them as well."],[5384,5601,"Another phone call?"],[5747,5855,"Hold, please."],[6056,6143,"Oh no..."],[6143,6210,"Just..."],[6210,6281,"What is it?"],[6281,6335,"Okay..."],[6406,6585,"It's just your secretary."],[6585,6798,"I told you Eve couldn't be..."],[6852,6948,"Boss, we're in trouble."],[6948,7140,"Every single company we've signed with,"],[7140,7236,"they're all suddenly"],[7236,7403,"cancelling their contracts with us."],[7403,7465,"No..."],[7465,7520,"What?"],[7728,7999,"No!"],[7999,8224,"No!"],[8224,8370,"No, no!"],[8391,8579,"Eve, how could you do this?"],[8612,8737,"How could you do this to me?"],[8737,8825,"Why?"],[8825,8996,"The humanity of it all!"]],"39":[[262,525,"You can't do this to me!"],[588,642,"You?"],[696,925,"You are so panicked."],[1001,1109,"Well, what happened?"],[1109,1188,"I thought that"],[1188,1368,"you said that you had it all under control"],[1368,1543,"and you didn't need anybody's finances."],[1601,1814,"Or did you have an idea this whole time"],[1814,2010,"that someone was helping you,"],[2010,2114,"but you..."],[2114,2331,"you might have just been too proud?"],[2448,2577,"Shawn Rockwell,"],[2644,2898,"you are a disappointment."],[3082,3244,"Shawn's supposed to be"],[3244,3378,"my golden goose."],[3378,3549,"I was gonna be rich."],[3549,3674,"I can't just let Eve"],[3674,3782,"take that away from me."],[3782,3849,"Eve!"],[3916,4166,"You are a cruel,"],[4166,4462,"soulless excuse of a woman!"],[4462,4662,"How could you do this to your husband?"],[4775,5017,"You have no right to talk."],[5125,5276,"Karen Bradley, you"],[5276,5392,"you forced my hand."],[5392,5584,"No, no, I... I did..."],[5584,5830,"I didn't and John didn't!"],[5897,6135,"Okay, you may not be all to blame."],[6164,6310,"I mean, after all, we know"],[6310,6439,"how he really is."],[6573,6681,"I mean he just would have"],[6681,6869,"gone to the next pretty thing"],[6869,6944,"if it wasn't for you."],[6944,7115,"But what you did"],[7115,7432,"is you came into my house"],[7453,7716,"and then you ruined my family"],[7716,7816,"and now"],[7816,7932,"you're sitting here"],[7932,8170,"having the audacity to"],[8170,8295,"call me cruel?"],[8408,8504,"Wait, look."],[8888,8975,"I know"],[9050,9188,"that I fucked up"],[9284,9442,"with the cheating"],[9501,9663,"and the divorce thing."],[9747,9884,"You know, but"],[9884,10164,"I had no idea that you were"],[10189,10385,"Queen Corbelle of the Red Carpet."],[10385,10618,"It's because Karen lied to me"],[10618,10727,"and you lied to me!"],[10727,10810,"Had I known that,"],[10810,11052,"I would never have cheated on you."],[11169,11327,"It's my fault?"],[11432,11607,"It's my fault"],[11607,11795,"that your ego is so delicate"],[11795,12095,"that I had to hide who I really was?"],[12149,12274,"It's my fault"],[12274,12504,"that you wanted me to quit my job"],[12504,12670,"so that I could stay home"],[12670,12783,"with the family."],[12783,13104,"It's my fault that I loved you so much,"],[13104,13254,"that I wanted to help you"],[13254,13434,"from behind the scenes."],[13534,13592,"You know what?"],[13592,13688,"Shawn Rockwell,"],[13709,13847,"you are the worst"],[13847,13993,"type of human being."],[13993,14164,"You are the type of person who blames"],[14164,14314,"everything on everyone else"],[14314,14372,"and doesn't want to"],[14372,14489,"take any accountability"],[14489,14689,"for anything they've ever done."],[14689,14881,"You repel me!"]],"40":[[91,196,"That's not true!"],[283,383,"That's not true!"],[408,479,"You were a liar."],[479,583,"You, you lied to me."],[583,679,"You never told me"],[679,746,"you went to college."],[746,900,"I didn't know you were an Ivy Leagueer."],[921,1021,"You just said you were"],[1021,1167,"some stupid,"],[1184,1351,"dumb little housewife."],[1468,1584,"Shawn Rockwell,"],[1584,1726,"you disgust me."],[1751,1876,"You know what, I'm so happy"],[1876,2047,"that she came into our lives."],[2077,2223,"To think that I might have been with you"],[2223,2364,"for another few years,"],[2364,2494,"another decade,"],[2615,2756,"it makes me so sick."],[2919,3065,"Okay, well..."],[3090,3261,"if that is the case,"],[3290,3470,"Queen Corbelle,"],[3524,3678,"do you think you could just"],[3707,3782,"forgive me?"],[3824,4024,"Just this once?"],[4070,4241,"Look, I'm here to run the"],[4241,4358,"Grand Maple Gala."],[4387,4529,"Okay, I don't have time"],[4529,4717,"to deal with this trash."],[4717,4934,"Security, please dispose of them."],[4967,5067,"You can't get rid of us."],[5067,5226,"No, I won't go."],[5271,5376,"Never gonna happen!"],[5384,5484,"Of course she can."],[5568,5743,"She's the Queen of the Red Carpet"],[5743,5901,"and this is her empire."],[6001,6247,"Eve, I... I... please..."],[6322,6514,"I mean, Queen Corbelle."],[6577,6810,"You can't just kick us out of here."],[6915,6998,"Security,"],[7123,7269,"get rid of these two immediately"],[7269,7403,"and get a good look at their faces"],[7403,7549,"because they are permanently banned"],[7549,7678,"from all future events."],[7786,7878,"No!"],[7878,8028,"You can't do this!"],[8270,8350,"Enough!"],[8350,8495,"Is that all you got, Giovanni?"],[8546,8708,"Leonardo is a hundred than that!"],[8729,8837,"I'll be back!"],[8837,9046,"This is not the last time you see me!"],[9088,9288,"No, no, no!"]],"41":[[133,283,"Now that we've taken out the trash,"],[333,496,"may I have the pleasure of a dance"],[496,600,"to end this"],[600,684,"crazy evening?"],[800,959,"Always an opportunist, Giovanni."],[959,1155,"It's not really the right time for that, is it?"],[1359,1488,"What are your plans for later?"],[1547,1685,"I'm thinking an after-party."],[1739,1885,"Exclusive invites only."],[1931,2106,"So no one can make you feel"],[2198,2277,"uncomfortable."],[2477,2556,"Lady,"],[2606,2740,"free to do what she pleases."],[2836,2994,"I don't think you get a say"],[2994,3078,"in her scheduling."],[3474,3532,"Eve,"],[3657,3745,"it's your choice."],[3778,3933,"That's what being Queen will"],[3933,4045,"do for you."],[4062,4279,"I mean Giovani Cavolini and"],[4279,4408,"Leonardo Harrington"],[4408,4537,"fighting over you."],[4537,4779,"They are the most eligible bachelors"],[4779,4884,"in this city."],[5000,5125,"What a woman!"],[5684,5755,"Hello?"],[5755,5834,"Eve!"],[5834,6047,"Or should I say, Queen Corbelle?"],[6064,6247,"I just heard the good news."],[6247,6406,"Now, it's alumni reunion week"],[6406,6535,"at Avenir Arts School,"],[6535,6723,"and we would love if you could come"],[6723,6856,"and be our keynote speaker"],[6856,6986,"as Queen Corbelle."],[6986,7111,"We have so many kids here"],[7111,7186,"that look up to you."],[7186,7265,"I'm..."],[7265,7432,"not really sure if that..."],[7474,7640,"Please, Eve, it's been so long."],[7640,7761,"We've all missed you."],[7937,8174,"Well, I was just there the other day,"],[8174,8270,"ironically,"],[8358,8504,"for a parent teacher conference."],[8504,8616,"My daughter,"],[8616,8767,"she actually goes to school there."],[8833,8925,"Eve,"],[8925,9059,"you never mentioned your daughter"],[9059,9159,"went to Avenir."],[9180,9292,"That settles it then."],[9292,9430,"You have to come, okay?"],[9430,9572,"Thursday, 3 P.M."],[9572,9672,"We're gonna have a speech"],[9672,9751,"from the Queen."],[9830,10026,"I'm retiring this year, Eve."],[10026,10089,"Please."],[10089,10218,"For old time's sake."],[10218,10352,"I'm counting on you."],[10623,10694,"Are you alright?"],[10998,11098,"If you don't want to do it,"],[11144,11361,"we could make an excuse."],[11473,11624,"No, it's... it's fine."],[11903,12012,"I mean, Miriam Marlett,"],[12012,12107,"she was there for me"],[12107,12203,"when I was a student,"],[12203,12303,"and I really..."],[12303,12424,"I don't mind doing it."],[12424,12512,"It's just that..."],[12771,12846,"I guess it's time"],[12846,12992,"I have a proper conversation"],[12992,13083,"with my daughter."]],"42":[[58,137,"Bullshit!"],[137,225,"Oh, John..."],[462,517,"Babe..."],[517,613,"Fuck off!"],[646,784,"Look what you've done to me!"],[800,905,"Oh, oh, yeah..."],[1034,1101,"Shawn!"],[1126,1217,"Please."],[1217,1347,"I love you."],[1347,1518,"I need you."],[1647,1764,"I need your money."],[1776,1893,"Once I get my hands on it,"],[1893,2127,"I'm leaving and never looking back."],[2177,2285,"And besides,"],[2285,2506,"it's not as bad as you think."],[2544,2673,"What do you mean?"],[2802,2890,"I mean"],[2932,3190,"Eve never gave us any real evidence,"],[3190,3253,"did she?"],[3265,3324,"I mean,"],[3324,3520,"she just showed us a picture of her"],[3520,3678,"with those huge sunglasses."],[3678,3803,"It's not that hard to fake."],[4483,4579,"Whatever short."],[5096,5167,"What does that mean?"],[5167,5251,"I don't... so what?"],[5263,5476,"Gigi followed Queen Corbelle"],[5476,5597,"to Paris 16 years ago."],[5597,5676,"She's been working on"],[5676,5805,"a secret documentary"],[5805,5897,"about Corbelle's life."],[5897,5993,"Hasn't been back since."],[5993,6068,"I'll ask her."],[6101,6264,"That doesn't prove anything"],[6264,6385,"and has nothing to do with this!"],[6385,6481,"Oh my God!"],[6619,6831,"Gigi was the MC"],[6831,6965,"at the Grand Maple Gala"],[6965,7115,"16 years ago."],[7144,7365,"She was Queen Corbelle's PA"],[7365,7490,"before she disappeared."],[7524,7720,"I'm college friends with her brother."],[7720,7907,"So if her brother is saying"],[7907,8028,"that she went to Paris"],[8028,8153,"and never came back..."],[8162,8329,"That means Queen Corbelle"],[8412,8562,"is still in Paris!"],[8637,8737,"She's still in Paris,"],[8737,8825,"which means"],[8825,8942,"that Queen Corbelle"],[8942,9050,"cannot be Eve!"],[9063,9154,"That's right!"],[9154,9363,"So we just need to get Gigi here"],[9363,9630,"and we can prove that Eve is a fake!"],[9688,9772,"We better get somebody else"],[9772,9813,"high up,"],[9813,9864,"yeah, as..."],[9864,9964,"like a witness."],[10018,10064,"Yeah."],[10064,10293,"Oh my God, Dad!"],[10326,10485,"Dean Marlett just announced"],[10485,10548,"we're gonna have"],[10548,10744,"a special guest speaker"],[10744,10910,"at our alumni event!"],[10940,11077,"She said it's someone"],[11077,11186,"very special"],[11211,11344,"with a ton of power"],[11344,11498,"in the fashion industry."],[11549,11669,"You're gonna be there right?"],[11695,11790,"And Karen?"],[11845,12057,"Fashion industry, that's very powerful."],[12057,12308,"That's exactly what we need."],[12383,12591,"I'll be there, dear, just for you."],[12654,12783,"And of course,"],[12783,13142,"I'd go anything for my darling Lily!"],[14139,14255,"Lily, Lily..."],[14372,14514,"What am I gonna do with you?"]],"43":[[79,125,"Eve,"],[221,425,"are you sure you're okay going in alone?"],[487,600,"I'm fine, Giovanni."],[617,709,"You have a board meeting"],[709,784,"in 30 minutes."],[784,900,"I think they need you more."],[1255,1447,"And that goes for you too, Leo."],[1447,1622,"You're supposed to be on set right now."],[1680,1801,"Okay, off you go."],[1822,1868,"See ya."],[1956,2043,"I'll..."],[2043,2135,"I'll pick you up later."],[2235,2318,"Don't worry, Eve."],[2364,2498,"When this board meeting's done,"],[2498,2660,"Shawn Rockwell will have to pay back"],[2660,2827,"every single cent he owes."],[3407,3628,"Wow, I wonder which one's her kid."],[3745,3837,"She's gorgeous."],[3858,3945,"And rich."],[3991,4120,"She's wearing the new ensemble"],[4120,4204,"of ROGUE."],[4220,4391,"Account for $20,000."],[4408,4466,"Hold on..."],[4592,4708,"Is she the guest speaker?"],[4959,5109,"Lily, isn't that your mom?"],[5309,5359,"What?"],[5417,5668,"She usually looks like such a slob!"],[5668,5885,"What is she all dressed up for?"],[5951,6056,"Holy..."],[6122,6214,"It is her!"],[6264,6322,"Mom?"],[6448,6548,"What are you doing here?"],[6577,6719,"I didn't say you could be here."],[6790,6894,"No, you didn't invite me."],[6956,7136,"But I got an invite from the Dean."],[7215,7278,"I'm the speaker."]],"44":[[0,237,"Wait, so when Dean Marlett said that"],[237,400,"there was gonna be a guest speaker,"],[400,542,"it's actually your mom?"],[575,721,"Lily, you never told us!"],[734,842,"Because it's not."],[842,925,"It's not her."],[925,1155,"I told you my mom is not special."],[1155,1209,"She's just"],[1209,1368,"a stay-at-home housewife."],[1418,1497,"Uh..."],[1497,1626,"What are you doing here?"],[1647,1697,"Get out!"],[1697,1764,"Go away!"],[1764,1868,"You're embarrassing me!"],[1947,2102,"Well, I can promise you, I am..."],[2139,2256,"definitely not lying."],[2356,2410,"Lily,"],[2448,2527,"come on, don't."],[2527,2648,"She's still your mom."],[2648,2777,"I'll say what I want."],[2777,2894,"And I think you're"],[2894,3069,"an old, useless, ugly"],[3069,3203,"piece of shit!"],[3203,3415,"You don't deserve me or Dad."],[3453,3641,"And I hate you!"],[3666,3782,"I would rather be dead"],[3782,3878,"than be your daughter."],[3903,3945,"So..."],[4058,4170,"who would you rather have"],[4170,4241,"to be your mom?"],[4350,4491,"Your dad's mistress?"],[4500,4604,"Uh, yeah!"],[4604,4742,"At least she's young and hot"],[4742,4867,"and does stuff for me."],[4884,4946,"Oh!"],[4946,5046,"What does she do for you"],[5046,51